{"tid":272424,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"CNN 拍假新聞片，CNN=Fake news","createTime":"2017-06-05T20:26:36.000Z","updateTime":"2017-06-07T04:51:23.000Z","uid":22054,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"e1fdfbcf73df6c608717ddac9d9a53e7b1a13ed7","tid":272424,"uid":22054,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-05T20:26:36.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/muME4lb7YhM\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FmuME4lb7YhM&d=Rq9gFWrYpwVjoItm5vmgSZZgE6vMW1KEzMhkvokIvkY%3D&h=ff551aa5\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/muME4lb7YhM</a>"},{"pid":"9c677eb108938b47d1dc1c0041799881f634eafa","tid":272424,"uid":20816,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-06T03:01:07.000Z","msg":"叫班回人企好都叫造假？"},{"pid":"72e7bcaf16e91cacc306aba57df3ae15356bc197","tid":272424,"uid":75326,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-07T04:51:23.000Z","msg":"國際中心 ／綜合報導<br />\n<br />\n一名自稱馬克（Mark）、推特帳號為@markantro的網友4日上傳一段影片，指控CNN拍攝假新聞，還在推文中寫道美國總統川普和其支持者最愛用的話題標籤「#FakeNews」（#假新聞）。影片中可見，CNN知名主持人貝琪安德森（Becky Anderson）與其採訪團隊當時在倫敦橋，正在拍攝一群譴責恐怖攻擊的穆斯林民眾。馬克認為這些人是被刻意安排到現場，故意塑造穆斯林關懷恐攻罹難者的形象。CNN駁斥這項指控，說這是在「胡扯」（nonsense）。<br />\n這些穆斯林在警方的協助之下，拿著寫有「IS將敗」「愛會獲勝」「致倫敦」等標語走到鏡頭前。CNN 和其他媒體如BBC和美聯社當時也在現場，CNN的發言人表示假新聞的傳言「完全是一派胡言。那群抗議民眾當時只是被警察允許穿過封鎖線，如此才能讓媒體拍攝他們手上的牌子。」<br />\n<br />\n▼ BBC也有報導這起抗議事件。（圖／翻攝自BBC新聞網）<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.ettoday.net/news/20170606/939145.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.ettoday.net%2Fnews%2F20170606%2F939145.htm&d=Rq9gFWrYpwVjoItm5vmgSZZgE6vMW1KEzMhkvokIvkY%3D&h=bbe2febf\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.ettoday.net/news/20170606/939145.htm</a>"}]}